        "segment": "status:-free",
        "alignment": "center",
        "html": "<p><em><strong>This is You Love To See It — a weekly feature reviewing good news, progress and action steps that’s one of the many features available only to </strong></em><strong>Lever</strong><em><strong> supporting subscribers. Thank you so much for being a supporting subscriber — we couldn’t do this reporting without your support.</strong></em></p>",
        "buttonText": "Click Here To Comment",
